name: BRANDY
description: Brandy was a curious blend of two well-loved icons from the Boy’s Club comics. When their digital essences combined, the result was Brandy—a creature who embodied the best of both worlds and became an inspiration for everyone. As Brandy engaged with fans, it naturally sparked discussions about everything from the latest trends to the best crypto in the market. BRANDY token launched at 20th of May 2025 is a meme token on the Solana blockchain.
